configurable values in etc/openerp.cfg from env variables? (number of workers...)
could just be some 'sed' commands, example:

in docker-compose.yml:

ODOO_CONF_WORKERS=4

in etc/openerp.cfg:

workers = ##ODOO_CONF_WORKERS##

in entrypoint.sh:

sed -i -e "s/##ODOO_CONF_WORKERS##/${ODOO_CONF_WORKERS:-4}/g" etc/openerp.cfg

